$interpreted: Puggi: Uh...little bit bored...
Puggi: Ah! I'll take something to Pang, whose been training in seclusion. If I remember correctly, his training location is...
Sharice: Puggi!!!!
Sharice: Give us back that Rune item that's on your head!
Puggi: Why all of a sudden? I still want to play.
Puggi: Well, if you want it, that's okay. But you need to promise...
Puggi: Wah! Why so angry? Isn't it normal to first say a few meaningless things, like Pang, and then get to the main point?
Angelia: Sione, there's no need to get right into fighting!
Sione: Looks to me like he's not going to cooperate. Rather than having him play with our minds, we ought to make the first move.
Puggi: Wahhh! Help me!!
Angelia: Sorry, Puggi. We really don't want to have to hurt you.
Angelia: But that Rune device recorded us playing in the water. In order to protect our reputation, you'll need to give it back.
Puggi: So what you're saying is...inside this device is a record of all you playing in the water wearing those skimpy outfits?
Puggi: Tell me. How do you think we all got to this point?
Puggi: Love? Courage? Friendship? It's none of these silly notions. It's all because of the support we've had from the players watching the screen right now.
Puggi: Inside this device are plenty of photos we can give back to the players as a gift. If you are going to be this selfish...well, I won't allow it!
Naya: What kind of word games is this rotten chicken playing?
Puggi: As the main character of this game, my mission in life is to publish these photos for everyone to see. I'll die before I hand them over!
Angelia: Eh? Why are we suddenly the bad guys?
Sharice: Whoopsies, I think I used a little too much force!
